    "type": 0,
    "content": "**Welcome to the Team Leader Registry!** 👋\n\nIf you are the designated leader of your team, please register here so we can assign you the Team Leader role. This role gives you access to post questions in #ask-mentors during the build sprint.\n\n💎 To register, post a single message with the following:\n\nYour full name\nYour team name\nNumber of team members\nTeam Members (tag them please)\n\n⚪ Example:\n\nMaría García — Team Nova — 3 members - team-tags\n\nOnce verified, we'll assign your role and you'll be all set. Only one team leader per team, please.\n\n**If you need to change your team's designated leader during the hackathon, let us know here and we'll update the role accordingly.**",
